question: Retrive all purchase details
query:
SELECT p.purchase_id, p.purchase_date, p.amount, p.registration_number,
       CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, c.email, c.address,
       b.manufacturer, b.model, b.price,
       d.dealer_name, d.location
FROM purchases p
INNER JOIN customers c ON p.customer_id = c.customer_id
INNER JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
INNER JOIN dealers d ON p.dealer_id = d.dealer_id;

SELECT c.customer_id, CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, c.email, c.phone_number, c.address
FROM customers c
INNER JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id
INNER JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
WHERE b.model = 'Pulsar NS 200';

SELECT c.customer_id, CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, c.email, c.phone_number, c.address
FROM customers c
INNER JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id
INNER JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
WHERE b.model = 'Livo';

SELECT c.customer_id, CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, c.email, c.phone_number, c.address
FROM customers c
INNER JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id
INNER JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
WHERE b.model = 'CT 125X';

SELECT c.customer_id, CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, c.email, c.phone_number, c.address
FROM customers c
INNER JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id
INNER JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
WHERE b.model = 'Apache RTR 200 4V';

SELECT c.customer_id, CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, c.email, c.phone_number, c.address
FROM customers c
INNER JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id
INNER JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
WHERE b.model = 'Shine 125';

question: Retrieve all dealers and the bike they have sold
query:
SELECT d.dealer_id, d.dealer_name, d.location, b.manufacturer, b.model, p.purchase_date,amount

SELECT d.dealer_name, SUM(p.amount) AS total_sales
FROM dealers d
INNER JOIN purchases p ON d.dealer_id = p.dealer_id
GROUP BY d.dealer_name;

question: Show me the total number of purchases made by each customer.
query:
SELECT c.customer_id, CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, COUNT(p.purchase_id) AS purchases_count
FROM customers c
LEFT JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id
GROUP BY c.customer_id, c.first_name, c.last_name;

question: Show me the latest purchases
query:

INNER JOIN purchases p ON d.dealer_id = p.dealer_id

question: Retrieve all purchases made by customers who live in Vijay Nagar
query:
SELECT p.purchase_id, p.purchase_date, p.amount, p.registration_number,
       CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, c.address
FROM purchases p
INNER JOIN customers c ON p.customer_id = c.customer_id
WHERE c.address LIKE '%vijay nagar%';

SELECT CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name,p.purchase_id, p.purchase_date,  p.registration_number, 
       b.manufacturer, b.model,b.price,p.amount
FROM purchases p
INNER JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
INNER JOIN customers c ON p.customer_id = c.customer_id
WHERE p.purchase_id ='11';

SELECT d.dealer_name, SUM(p.amount) AS total_revenue
FROM purchases p
INNER JOIN dealers d ON p.dealer_id = d.dealer_id
WHERE d.dealer_name = 'Honda Bigwing'
GROUP BY d.dealer_name
order by SUM(p.amount) desc ;

question: How much money has each customer spent and how many bikes do they own
query:
SELECT CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, SUM(p.amount) AS total_amount_spent, count(b.bike_id) AS bikes_owned
FROM customers c
JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id
JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
GROUP BY customer_name;

SELECT CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, SUM(p.amount) AS total_amount_spent, count(b.bike_id) AS bikes_owned
FROM customers c
JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id
JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
WHERE c.first_name = 'Saurav' and c.last_name = 'Jain'
GROUP BY customer_name;
